{"tid":178369,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"【改詞】Passengers：溺水的人總想拖人落水","createTime":"2017-03-29T13:25:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-02T07:46:59.000Z","uid":37464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"040571ffa33e2458ce22833e87a65d0952b1135e","tid":178369,"uid":37464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:25:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://youtu.be/yK8GQKESCbI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyK8GQKESCbI&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWuargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=5313b71d\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/yK8GQKESCbI</a><br />\n<br />\n原詞：林日曦<br />\n作曲：鄧智偉<br />\n填詞：DC_<br />\n演唱：Kalista<br />\n歌名：Passengers<br />\n<br />\n穿梭於太空　航道裡看透星空<br />\n哪怕相差的光年　也甘願沉睡入眠<br />\n然而這個歷練　無力可改變<br />\n誰願早起數十年<br />\n<br />\n得一個人　年月裡每秒空等<br />\n訴說不甘的感言　卻只讓寧靜蔓延<br />\n祈求蒼天垂憐　為我設置伏線<br />\n無奈這一年　仍撩動我的底線<br />\n<br />\n人生　明明是星海微塵<br />\n何苦　竟想到未來做眾神<br />\n如今　存活像荒島游魂<br />\n從此　只等髮白承受駭聞<br />\n偏偏卻遇上你如藥引　當事成後會難蒙混<br />\n我　也想繼續靠近　尋覓你封印<br />\n<br />\n遺留家鄉來尋夢　盼與你去目送<br />\n沒法去包容　才明白你的心痛<br />\n<br />\n誰想　流連在星空浮沈<br />\n留低　機艙卻未曾遇見人<br />\n如果　能伴著一起同行<br />\n從此　幾多際遇無懼見聞<br />\n終於信任破了難步近　心　就如犯罪而懷恨<br />\n你已不會願答允陪伴我紓困<br />\n<br />\n倘若倒轉誰喚我　將事情脈絡呈來問<br />\n我也不會願答允陪伴你紓困"},{"pid":"0cd1bb449c2c0747d15313b342345b7644f9c162","tid":178369,"uid":90596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:58:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eb2c658365442d2c34c04c03c0a57a96e2a7595","tid":178369,"uid":41326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:08:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c110f8895238e73b854b17bc3244dd535770ae","tid":178369,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:10:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63cab6ff5a2313d0ee80800b43ffdf979e9423a","tid":178369,"uid":4042